        </view>
        <view class="goodsItem">
          <image src="http://www.zhangxiaode.com/wxImgs/乌梅.jpg"></image>
          <view class="goodsName">椒麻鸡</view>
          <view class="goodsPrice">¥98.00</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="goCarte">进入菜单</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section personal">
      <view class="sectionHd">会员详情</view>
      <view class="weLevel">
        <view class="wel">欢迎回来，金风凝香</view>
        <view class="level">
          <view class="levelIcon">
            <image src="../../assets/levelIcon.svg"></image>
          </view>
          <text>平民</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="score">我在本店成长值267分，升级还需1193分</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section shopDetail">
      <view class="sectionHd">会员详情</view>
      <view class="banner">
        <image src="http://www.zhangxiaode.com/wxImgs/乌梅.jpg"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="shopIntro">餐厅坐落在仙境般的西溪湿地s生态公园,让顾客在品尝美味同时也可以欣赏西溪湿地的美丽景色</view>
      <view class="shopWrap">
        <arrowBtn wx:for="{{shopInfo}}" wx:key="index" arrowData="{{item}}" bindtap="goAbout"></arrowBtn>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="evaluate">
    </view>
    <view class="copyRight">
    </view>
    <view class="goPay">
    </view>
  </scroll-view>
